THREE young men were arrested at a pastor’s house in Mokhurumela Village, outside Bochum in Limpopo. They were charged with kidnapping, murder and attempted murder. The suspects are accused of kidnapping and assaulting Frederick Raletjena (29) and Hector Teffo (26). The victims were found by a passerby and rushed to hospital, where Raletjena died two days later. According to Limpopo police spokesman Brigadier Motlafela Mojapelo, the two men were dumped in the bush about 20km from their homes after being assaulted. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstCKvVqS44yk_3ae2wuRM76mKD3ZzZ86XiHP7KF-BnhsMmJljL_9pRXZHHo3Hr2RidbgUbZWXyZ63DKjLjrRKKSramL2Uy4BZO8vHOQsQunV5QyqePeea66i7T473MNB70B8c9Mq-cyoNarQ5HAlH9df3nhj6JCGp_b5Lhs4R8NHo-yPLKV1hwRi7FyRPmYGHbEbH2WqYcv9ukRl_Eiyt-bVcgnhKTUkGPkp0S9k5qGir2CVRdUXAa2oL_5LHMEBVzZ_RiYgWyWZ_amRIoR9dlqxQJkwNg\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzFoFCWFstk5OEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
